{"tid":657001,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"5月尾6月頭波蘭旅行求助","createTime":"2018-05-07T17:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T09:11:25.000Z","uid":68443,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"c44af6c0e43bf376abe6648f3a2c021d35e0dd1e","tid":657001,"uid":68443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-07T17:11:22.000Z","msg":"是咁的,各位巴絲打<br />\n<br />\n小弟計畫5月尾至6月頭飛波蘭<br />\n主要遊博物館,名勝,古蹟<br />\n來回都係華沙<br />\n目前行程如下:<br />\n<br />\n華沙:<br />\nDay1: 落地,check in,視乎抵達時間行舊城區<br />\nDay2: 華沙起義博物館<br />\nDay3: 華沙猶太人歷史博物館<br />\nDay4: 市內遊覽/行多個博物館<br />\n<br />\n克拉科夫:<br />\nDay1: 市內名勝<br />\nDay2: 奧斯威辛<br />\nDay3: 鹽礦<br />\nDay4: Zakopane<br />\nDay5: 再行市內名勝<br />\n<br />\nGdansk:<br />\nDay1: 市內遊覽<br />\nDay2: Sopot<br />\nDay3: Malbork Castle<br />\n<br />\n我預留14日13夜<br />\n我發現波蘭內陸航班<br />\n價錢唔算貴,但好慳時間<br />\n<br />\n由於無長時間遠遊經驗,亦無去過波蘭<br />\n希望咁多位巴絲求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e930247d412e81406a4e8d307ed43c8fc4c9cd0e","tid":657001,"uid":3206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T03:13:02.000Z","msg":"搵下有冇過夜巴  又平又慳時間"},{"pid":"8e19af3a273b50c672a6e372d4fccd62eb157e0f","tid":657001,"uid":130595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T03:22:12.000Z","msg":"krakow 都去到咁多日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我之前都係3晚<br />\n果陣仲係old town 間7仔買煙溝到個收銀妹妹, 約到佢夜晚食飯再帶返apartment <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bed8178a775fc9514b019c162cabe8e232f9c4d","tid":657001,"uid":26823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T03:27:14.000Z","msg":"Warsaw好悶 一般大城市咁"},{"pid":"cfac4ebdbbaac0310f911d68783db4b82397acbe","tid":657001,"uid":38212,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T03:31:16.000Z","msg":"polski bus"},{"pid":"a16a86560532eac9504d3bea8c4bc719a4cd83ce"